Source:  Oxford Book of NZ Plants
Author:  MOORE & IRWIN
Vol / Page:  174
Edition:
Quote:  <i>HEBE HULKEANA </i>. The `Marlborough lilac' grows on limestone bluffs from the Conway River northwards as a bush half to one metre tall ... and flowers range from pinkish lavender to white.
